= Changqing Fu 

~~~
{}{img_left}{pic/pic.jpg}{Profile Pic}{200}{200}{}

*Research Interests*: Computer Vision and Machine Learning

Welcome! I'm a senior-year PhD student in CEREMADE, University of Paris IX Dauphine - PSL, fortunately advised by Prof. [https://www.ceremade.dauphine.fr/~cohen/ Laurent Cohen]. Before that I was a graduate student in University at Albany, State University of New York advised by Prof. [https://www.albany.edu/~yy298919/ Yiming Ying]. I recieved a Bachelor's degree from School of Mathematical Sciences in Fudan University advised by Prof. [https://mastone1983.github.io/ Lei Shi], and a Master's degree in Theoretical and Applied Mathematics from Paris IX - PSL advised by [https://www.ceremade.dauphine.fr/~mula/ Olga Mula] and [https://sites.google.com/site/robryd/ Robin Ryder]. 

Here are my [https://prairie-institute.fr/chairs/fu-changqing/ Institutional Page], [pdf/CV.pdf CV], [https://github.com/EvergreenTree GitHub], [Twitter https://twitter.com/evergreencqfu] and [http://www.linkedin.com/in/cqfu-fdu Linkedin].

*Email*: cfu_at_ceremade_dot_dauphine_dot_fr
